HEADWORD: Incommutable
<hw>In`com*mut"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>incommutabilis</ets>: cf. F. <ets>incommutable</ets>. See
<er>In-</er> not, and <er>Commutable</er>.]</ety> <def>Not commutable;
not capable of being exchanged with, or substituted for, another.</def>
<au>Cudworth.</au> -- <wordforms><wf>In`com*mut"a*ble*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos> -- <wf>In`com*mut"a*bly</wf>,
